11 SUMMARY
1122 This amendment is the majority report of the committee. The amendment specifies
1133 that the persons to be added to the 1998 Special Plan of the Maine Public Employees
1144 Retirement System under this legislation are employees of the Department of Health and
1155 Human Services employed on October 1, 2025 or hired thereafter who are in the Mental
1166 Health Worker I job classification, the Mental Health Worker II job classification, the
1177 Mental Health Worker III job classification or the Mental Health Worker IV job
1188 classification.
1199 FISCAL NOTE REQUIRED
2200 (See attached)
